---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en" class="grid-overlay">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>NeuroLogix Privacy Energy Matrix</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="privacy">
      <header class="privacy__hero">
        <div class="privacy__halo pulse-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="privacy__content">
          <p class="privacy__pre">Neurologix Compliance Signal</p>
          <h1>Use of Privacy Collection Grid</h1>
          <p>
            NeuroLogix collects and orchestrates operational data with luminous precision. This page
            maps how every photon of information flows, why it is charged, and the protections that
            guard its journey across the Veralogix lattice.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="privacy__matrix">
        <h2>Data Streams We Capture</h2>
        <div class="privacy__grid">
          <article class="privacy__card">
            <h3>Engagement Beacons</h3>
            <p>
              Signals from onboarding forms, concierge dialogues, and support tickets. Each entry is
              timestamped and encrypted before it touches the NeuroLogix core.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="privacy__card">
            <h3>Operational Telemetry</h3>
            <p>
              Workflow metadata, automation triggers, and agent performance metrics collected to
              tune efficiency and stability fields across your enterprise nodes.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="privacy__card">
            <h3>Compliance Credentials</h3>
            <p>
              Role-based access keys, audit confirmations, and consent receipts. These are isolated
              in hardened vaults with adaptive glow-based anomaly detection.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="privacy__use">
        <h2>Why the Energy is Harvested</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Service Activation:</strong> initiate tailored agent protocols and keep your
            command center synchronized in real time.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Experience Refinement:</strong> pulse anonymized diagnostics through our design
            loops to intensify usability, clarity, and response speeds.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Risk Mitigation:</strong> detect intrusions, fraud, or policy drift via spectral
            analytics and automated compliance alarms.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="privacy__consent">
        <div class="privacy__consent-shell">
          <h2>Consent & Control Switches</h2>
          <p>
            You command your data flux. Adjust preferences, revoke specific access points, or
            request deletion by signaling the concierge channel. We respond within 72 hours with a
            full audit trail of the action taken.
          </p>
          <div class="privacy__actions">
            <a class="cta" href="mailto:privacy@veralogix.ai">Request Data Pulse</a>
            <a class="cta cta--ghost" href="mailto:hello@veralogix.ai">Concierge Support</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="privacy__guardians">
        <h2>How We Secure the Signal</h2>
        <div class="privacy__grid privacy__grid--dual">
          <article class="privacy__card">
            <h3>Layered Shielding</h3>
            <p>
              Multi-region redundancy, hardware encryption modules, and zero-trust network access
              enforce persistent glow barriers around sensitive clusters.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="privacy__card">
            <h3>Human Oversight</h3>
            <p>
              Certified compliance engineers review alerts, calibrate access rules, and document
              every escalation in immutable ledgers.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="privacy__footer">
        <p>
          For regulatory inquiries or partnership reviews, contact our Security Compliance Guard at
          <a href="mailto:compliance@veralogix.ai">compliance@veralogix.ai</a>. All transmissions
          are monitored through encrypted glow channels.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .privacy {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
  }

  .privacy__hero {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.35);
    border-radius: 2.4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(6, 16, 12, 0.92), rgba(3, 10, 8, 0.72));
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .privacy__halo {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -30% -20% 10% 55%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.55), transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .privacy__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .privacy__pre {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240, 255, 245, 0.6);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  .privacy__matrix,
  .privacy__use,
  .privacy__guardians {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .privacy__matrix h2,
  .privacy__use h2,
  .privacy__guardians h2,
  .privacy__consent h2 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .privacy__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .privacy__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .privacy__grid--dual {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .privacy__card {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.25);
    border-radius: 1.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(6, 18, 13, 0.85), rgba(4, 10, 8, 0.75));
    padding: 1.75rem;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.08);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease, border 0.4s ease;
  }

  .privacy__card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -120% 30% 40% -60%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.15), transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: rotate(8deg);
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  .privacy__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.55);
    box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.45), 0 0 85px rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.25);
  }

  .privacy__card:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .privacy__card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .privacy__card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy__use ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .privacy__use li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy__use li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.8rem;
    width: 0.75rem;
    height: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.7);
  }

  .privacy__consent {
    position: relative;
  }

  .privacy__consent-shell {
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.4);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(7, 20, 14, 0.92), rgba(3, 10, 8, 0.72));
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.8rem;
  }

  .privacy__consent p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .privacy__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .privacy__guardians {
    border: 1px solid rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.32);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(5, 14, 10, 0.9), rgba(3, 9, 7, 0.68));
  }

  .privacy__footer {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy__footer a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 0.12em;
    text-underline-offset: 0.35em;
    transition: text-shadow 0.4s ease;
  }

  .privacy__footer a:hover {
    text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(55, 255, 159, 0.6);
  }
</style>
